v2.2: February, 2008
    * The mode constants were rewriten as class constants.
    * The hash support was removed.
    * The class attributes and methods were renamed based on PEAR Coding Standards.
    * The Crypt::MODE_HEX was improved and now the resulting string is shorter of the last version.
    * The class file was renamed to Crypt.php instead of the Crypt.class.php of the last version.

v2.1: August, 2007
    * Crypt class released on http://code.google.com
